@startuml
title Application Registration and File Import Process

participant Operator
participant System
participant "Application File Bot" as Bot

== Operator Initiated Registration ==
Operator -> System: Initiate registration process
System -> Operator: Prompt to select shared folder

== Automatic Data Import ==
System -> Bot: Import data
Bot --> System: Imported data

== Template File Generation and Submission ==
System -> Operator: Generate template file
Operator -> Operator: Fill in required data
Operator -> System: Submit template file

== Evaluation and Verification ==
System -> System: Evaluate application
System --> Operator: Application status

== Recording in the System ==
System -> System: Record application submission
System -> System: Import and store files
System --> Operator: Confirmation

@enduml
